author: COMSOL
description: In this innovative example, researchers zoom in flow in porous media by solving Navier–Stokes equations within individual pores. The model geometry (micrometer scale) comes from scanning electron microscope images of thinly sliced rock. How the variability in interstitial velocities upscale to continuum flows is of interest.
